  "texts": [
    "In contrast, gustatory preferences tend to be more stable and consistent across populations, primarily because they align closely with biological imperatives.",
    "The universal preference for sweet foods exemplifies this consistency, even as specific flavor nuances may vary across cultures.",
    "These distinctions in olfactory and gustatory interactions inform market strategies and product development in significant ways.",
    "In the olfactory domain, branding often incorporates scent marketing, using specific aromas to elicit emotional responses and establish a strong brand identity.",
    "For instance, calming scents in retail establishments can enhance the shopping experience and potentially boost sales."
